title: Listen Live: High school football - Bacon at Fitch
text:
Listen Live: High school football - Bacon at Fitch Published October 23. 2015 6:20PM Updated October 23. 2015 9:39PM 
Both Bacon Academy and Fitch boast 4-1 overall records and 3-0 records in the ECC Large. Tonight's winner will take sole possession of first place in the division.
